I stand before you today, pleading guilty to the offense of shoplifting a dress worth approximately 2000 pounds. I recognize the gravity of my actions and the impact they have on the victim and society as a whole. While I acknowledge the seriousness of my offense, I hope to shed light on certain mitigating factors that should be taken into consideration.

